de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface ResourceTypeModifierLevel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceConsumerA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceTypeModifierLevelImpl

    public interface ResourceTypeModifierLevel
extends ElementA, ResourceConsumerA
    A representation of the model object 'Resource Type Modifier Level'. A possible instance of a modifier, e.g. 250mA for a current level modifier.

    The following features are supported:

    • Equal Alternatives
    • Better Alternative
    See Also:
    LibraryPackage.getResourceTypeModifierLevel()
